information: The company ED. FITSCHER G.M.B.H. + CO. K.G. METALL- UND EISENGIESSEREI MASCHINENFABRIK, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1899, which operates in the Ores, ferrous and non-ferrous industry. It also operates in the Non-ferrous metal ores, Steel, Iron, special grade and pig iron, and Aluminium and aluminium alloys industries. It is based in Oberhausen, Germany.
